Screen Gems Logo Screen Gems, Inc. is an American film production and distribution studio that is a division of Sony Pictures’s Sony Pictures Entertainment Motion Picture Group, a subsidiary of Japanese multinational conglomerate, Sony Group Corporation. It has served several different purposes for its parent companies over the decades since its incorporation. The label currently specializes in genre films, mainly horror. Source
